From: Sven Schnelle <svens@linux.ibm.com>
Date: Tue, 8 Sep 2020 10:14:00 +0200
Subject: s390/stp: use u32 instead of unsigned int
Git-commit: 4ab79ed223d2ff32ffe16cfd841e064199341c34
Patch-mainline: v5.10-rc1
References: jsc#SLE-13821

In hardware-dependent headers using u32 is easier
to read and less error-prone.

